{"tid":99950,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本青森行程一問","createTime":"2017-01-29T15:10:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T02:56:29.000Z","uid":26426,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"acab9cd5a68b6903510d7a9177adfc9d8eff30ff","tid":99950,"uid":26426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:10:32.000Z","msg":"小弟四月尾會去青森玩<br />\n青森市內加弘前一日玩曬會唔會好趕<br />\n青森市-睡魔館 古川市場  A-factory 觀景台 市立美術館<br />\n弘前市-弘前城 弘前公園Starbuck <br />\n求巴打比下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36b66fc1a5b1af0c365d628e54230339fb3e57e","tid":99950,"uid":26426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d3fc96cd7b83de54b800868487aaa803f855cd","tid":99950,"uid":35196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T20:01:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絕對唔會 青森無乜野睇其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b7449120d7ee7817e55c2d11cff90182a570922","tid":99950,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:22:39.000Z","msg":"上次去剩係睇隻八甲田丸都用左半日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c65c0f9aa449e2dbb95fa1e0d36c5b08736392","tid":99950,"uid":57827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T04:34:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絕對唔會 青森無乜野睇其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁係你唔識搵野睇啫<br />\n<br />\n反而弘前真係冇乜野睇"},{"pid":"8555fe1e56574203660001fab3d8ec30f60e6101","tid":99950,"uid":51747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T13:21:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絕對唔會 青森無乜野睇其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁係你唔識搵野睇啫<br />\n<br />\n反而弘前真係冇乜野睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同老母去摘蘋果都半日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （巴士班次問題）<br />\n<br />\n睡魔館一個鐘夠啦，其實無乜展品。A FACTORY睇下食唔食飯，如果唔係未係買下野。ASPAM可以上去展望台睇夜景，如果唔係地下都係土產店。古川市場都係食つけ丼，無乜野行。市立美術館？定県立？搭車去都要時間，雖然可能淨係睇隻狗。去開其實又可以去埋三內丸山遺跡<br />\n<br />\n淨係市內景點計，兩日趕趕地差唔多（入黑就悶啲）"},{"pid":"2c5e6f506a9d03d675432268e3bd7332e02b46ff","tid":99950,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:28:29.000Z","msg":"其實無野睇，半日行哂2個跟住去左青葉城遺址"},{"pid":"ca3298ee70eeabbc63b98cbe0e888aad70ec2edb","tid":99950,"uid":26426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T00:46:05.000Z","msg":"咁一日玩曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留多d時間去奧入瀨"},{"pid":"9f43989d745f0cdf24e58418ccbb3a5a0e6c8ba8","tid":99950,"uid":64354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T02:19:38.000Z","msg":"青森市內無咩特別<br />\n反而弘前幾有特式 弘前城加Starbucks 都推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲有弘前駅前有d mall都值得行下<br />\n<br />\n想問問會唔會自駕 如果自駕就去埋十和田湖同奧入瀨溪流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df654d89ddc2f1ee768e54edf199d924b00790b","tid":99950,"uid":26426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T09:25:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>青森市內無咩特別<br />\n反而弘前幾有特式 弘前城加Starbucks 都推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲有弘前駅前有d mall都值得行下<br />\n<br />\n想問問會唔會自駕 如果自駕就去埋十和田湖同奧入瀨溪流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會自駕 不過會搭jr bus入奧入瀨溪流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBook左星野"},{"pid":"f1f9f4544289181e488a9a9d0f8bce1dbb3215aa","tid":99950,"uid":192846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T02:56:29.000Z","msg":"青森去過<br />\n真係好撚悶"}]}